{"title":"新非洲","authors":["拜·特·穆尔"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新非洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔利比里亚〕拜·特·穆尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲破沉沉黑夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲从东方升起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在全世界的报纸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲成了重要消息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你举目四望——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论北方和南方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论西方和东方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处是炮声隆隆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤醒了沉睡的土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殖民地迅速得到解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民甚至来不及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选择国歌和国旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们要使非洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使“黑大陆”彻底改观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的事业伟大无比。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，二万万人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二万万非洲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己掌握着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的命运。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些不久以前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使非洲血流成河的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论他们使用什么阴谋诡计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不能阻挡非洲的脚步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殖民主义者的监狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天变成了大学。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为自由斗争的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久经锻炼的英勇战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此走上了历史的舞台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们是红色的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们使所有的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对非洲刮目相视。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，非洲一定能赶上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的二十世纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔江枫、于火　译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}